	<%= render 'system_logs/system_logs' %>
</div>

<div id="show-priviledges" class="empl-opts">
	<button class="dash-bttn-help" id="help-priviledges">?</button>
	<% if current_employee.is_admin? %>
		<p class="employee-links" style="text-align:center;"> You have Administrative Priviledges on the system </p>
	<% else %>
		<p class="employee-links" style="text-align:center;"> Please contact an administrator for more priviledges</p>
	<% end %>
	<div  id="edit-empl" class="priv-opts">
		<%= render 'employees/edit_employee' %>
	</div>
	<div id="upload-empl" class="priv-opts">
		<%= render 'nemabollon_files/upload_memos' %>
	</div>

	<div  id="all-memos-empl" class="priv-opts">
		<%= render 'nemabollon_files/all_memos' %>
	</div>


	<button class="dash-bttn" id="edit-empl-acct">Edit Account </button>
	<button class="dash-bttn" id="upload-empl-files">Upload File </button>
	<button class="dash-bttn" id="show-all-files">All Files </button>
</div>

<div id="create-club-update" class="empl-opts">
	<button class="dash-bttn-help" id="help-club-update">?</button>
	<%= render 'club_updates/club_update_form' %>
</div>

</div>

</div>
</div>


<div class="help" id="h-calendar">
	<p> Welcome to the System Calendar.</p>
	<p> This is where all employees will list their tasks and objectives. It is also where all meetings will be shown. </p>
	<p> It is a valuable resource in keeping track of your own tasks and other tasks in the system. </p>
	<p> Every employee is expected to add their weekly tasks to the calendar and mark them as completed once they are complete. </p>
	<p> The Calendar also allows upper management to interact and track different orders of business on the system. </p>
	<h4> USING THE CALENDAR </h4>
	<p> Click any month to reveal the tasks and other options for that month </p>
	<p> Use the interface to add your own tasks and update your progress which will be reflected on the calendar </p>
</div>
<div class="help" id="h-add-employee">
	<p> Welcome to the Add Employee Interface </p>
	<p> This is the interface HR uses to add new Employee Accounts to the system. </p>

</div>
<div class="help" id="h-show-investors">
	<p> View all Investors </p>
	<p> This interface allows you to view all investors in the system. Some details are priviledged and only accessible to the Employees with appropriate credentials. </p>
	<p> If you are unable to find what you are searching for please contact a supervisor.</p>
</div>
<div class="help" id="h-updates">
	<p> View all Company Updates </p>
	<p> This interface allows you to view all company news and updates in the system. </p>
</div>
<div class="help" id="h-show-clubs">
	<p> View all Clubs </p>
	<p> This interface allows you to view all Clubs in the system.</p>
	<p> The Clubs are the core of the application. These are the investments made by the Investors into projects.</p>
	<p> The Clubs are made up of Projects that are owned by Beneficiaries. The Beneficiaries use their approved Project Applications to apply for Funding which they are credited from the Club. </p>
</div>
<div class="help" id="h-show-highlights">
	<p> View Application Highlights </p>
	<p> This interface allows you to add highlights which are posted to the home page. </p>
	<p> These highlights reflect the best news to share with the world. </p>
</div>
<div class="help" id="h-show-employees">
	<p> View All Employees </p>
	<p> This interface allows you to view all Employees in the system. </p>
</div>
<div class="help" id="h-country-managers">
		<p> View All Country Managers </p>
	<p> This interface allows you to view all Country Managers in the system. </p>
</div>

<div class="help" id="h-all-beneficiaries">
		<p> View All Beneficiaries </p>
	<p> This interface allows you to view all Beneficiaries in the system. </p>
</div>
<div class="help" id="h-show-proposals">
		<p> View All Proposals </p>
	<p> This interface allows you to view all Proposals in the system. </p>
</div>
<div class="help" id="h-system-logs">
		<p> View System Logs </p>
	<p> This interface allows you to view all the activity in the system. </p>
</div>
<div class="help" id="h-priviledges">
		<p> View My Priviledges</p>
	<p> This interface allows you to know what actions you may perform on the system. </p>
</div>